<div class="container justify-content-md-center">
  <div class="row justify-content-center g-lg-5 py-5">

    <h1 class="text-center mentalHealth "> Welcome {{user.first_name}} {{user.last_name}}</h1>

    <p class="typeFace">
      The Dialectical Behavioral Therapy (DBT) Diary Card below can be used as a treatment solution for those who need
      to regulate their emotions and mental health. It can help those diagnosed with borderline personality disorder,
      anxiety, and depression as well. You can fill out the diary card by rating the emotions you have experinced
      throughout the day or days past.The diary card is also used to keep track of where you are with thoughts about
      self harm.
    </p>
    <a href="./ask"><Button class="btn btnColor btn-lg">DBT Diary Card</Button></a>

    <p class="typeFace">
      Select the option below to access your past DBT Diary Cards so that you may either print them out for your
      therapist or save them on your computer for your own use.
    </p>

    <div class="dropdown">
      <button class="btn btnColor btn-lg dropdown-toggle" type="button" id="dropdownMenuButton1" data-bs-toggle="dropdown"
        aria-expanded="false">
        Past DBT Form
      </button>
      <ul class="dropdown-menu" aria-labelledby="dropdownMenuButton1">
        {{#each user.Data}}
        <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="/form/{{id}}">{{date}}</a></li>
        {{/each}}
      </ul>

    </div>

    <a href="./form"><Button class="btn btnColor btn-lg">Past DBT Diary Card</Button></a>
    <a href="./chart"><Button class="btn btnColor btn-lg">Data Analytics</Button></a>



  </div>
</div>
